      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CAKE IN TUMMY (6) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (16.43) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Should be very hard to beat this time. TIANA BANANA (3) missed the frame last time when fourth (16.81) at this track but prior to that had three placings in a row. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. EPIC MARCELINE (8) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5 lengths into third (16.72) at this track in a Grade 6 over 275m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Well-placed to take this out. OUR BOY DOUG (2) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
